Package: multiRF
Type: Package
Title: MRF-Based Multi-Omics Integration and Clustering
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Wei Zhang
Maintainer: Wei Zhang <wzhang1960@gmail.com>
Authors@R: 
    person("Wei", "Zhang", email = "wzhang1960@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for model-based integration of multi-omics datasets using
    random forests and Markov random field inspired weighting. The package
    provides workflows for model fitting, variable importance aggregation,
    clustering, and visualization.
